{"tid":786191,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"裝修完唔滿意 好唔開心","createTime":"2018-08-19T17:46:00.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-21T22:15:26.000Z","uid":73171,"like":6,"dislike":29,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"add6790fbc79385ea2bc5a316311f079fcf9a6e0","tid":786191,"uid":73171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T17:46:00.000Z","msg":"啱啱屋企裝修完，我間房啲入牆櫃同書檯嘅size同擺位完全唔啱心水唔舒服，搞到我好sad好失落，因為我覺得我間房係返工以外留得最多嘅地方，係我唯一享受生活嘅空間，所以我好執著，好在意。<br />\n<br />\n如果要改，就要將啲新嘅入牆櫃同書檯拆曬再造過，要比多啲錢同製造浪費。<br />\n<br />\n如果唔改，我會過得唔開心，呢幾晚未搬返入去已經失眠。<br />\n<br />\n大家覺得我係咪太固執？定係覺得唔鍾意就要改，最緊要住得舒服？<br />\n<br />\n利申：first world problem, 不喜勿插<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"698d26b33d23c1689e07920bca0bc0aec150e25e","tid":786191,"uid":115441,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T17:48:36.000Z","msg":"梗係改<br />\n因為趁而家裝修開可以一次過整埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"354748016f5850a9fcb932700715784b79833f59","tid":786191,"uid":177089,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T17:48:56.000Z","msg":"想改咪改囉 又唔係俾我地住 我地想唔想改關你咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b20b9ad6d6a5598b34a6cf63ecff4df3095c6243","tid":786191,"uid":21782,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T17:52:04.000Z","msg":"唔係本身根據左你意願先裝修架咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8a83159891af37446d2cfa642771c147f10d524","tid":786191,"uid":73171,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"698d26b33d23c1689e07920bca0bc0aec150e25e","tid":786191,"uid":115441,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T17:48:36.000Z","msg":"梗係改<br />\n因為趁而家裝修開可以一次過整埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T17:52:17.000Z","msg":"其實已經裝修完，我老豆老母都已經住緊，我前排出咗國，所以到尋日先第一次睇到我間房，發覺同我要求/想像差好遠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" clas